    "title": "Principal Frontend Developer at Byju's International Enterprises",
    "description": "We at Byju's International Enterprises are looking for an experienced Frontend Developer based out of Ranchi. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Byju's International Enterprises:\nByju's International Enterprises is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Learning & development budget\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Byju's International Enterprises!",
